{"tid":1869433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（多難興邦）254家外企捐中国   美國企業捐最多逾16億","createTime":"2020-02-08T07:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T13:21:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d360dc2c9c09b24cd66acfd230d8669697c1d527","tid":1869433,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎疫情延燒，美國務卿蓬佩奧宣布，將投入1億美元，協助中國等其他國家對抗新型冠狀病毒，另據中國第三方機構「責任雲研究院」統計，目前有254家外資企業捐贈現金和物資，當中美國企業捐最多，累計捐贈3.84億元人民幣（約16.79億元新台幣）現金和物資，佔整體27.9%。<br />\n<br />\n中國媒體《21世紀經濟報導》指出，中國社科院鐘宏武教授、責任雲研究院執行院長葉柳紅、研究員柳夢笛統計，截至6日，共有254家外資企業累計捐贈13.78億元人民幣（約60.25億元新台幣）現金和物資，美國、香港和南韓企業捐贈額居前3，當中又以美國企業捐最多，74家美企累計捐贈3.84億元人民幣現金和物資，佔整體27.9%。<br />\n<br />\n美國捐贈前10的企業依序為：Citadel、惠氏營養品中國、AO史密斯、GE、雅培中國、安利，丹納赫集團，百威中國、艾伯維，而NBA和NIKE並列第10。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/3061825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3061825&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=7ed76295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3061825&h=577a96b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/3061825</a>"},{"pid":"3e87294c2f59c54c30b5bcbd6ce86ecacb85d9e8","tid":1869433,"uid":223233,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:31:28.000Z","msg":"國家已經冇救，仲唔貪埋呢一筆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6671a06be126daa29dbafc41085b0a66ee21d2bd","tid":1869433,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hofu4kV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHofu4kV.jpg&h=6aa0a257&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d5e365bb9c2ece022ae2df034b69e6b421c0677","tid":1869433,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:02:37.000Z","msg":"沒有美國"},{"pid":"e959835dd08